<P>TWO SERMONS, DELIVERED BEFORE THE NEW-YORK MISSIONARY SOCIETY.</P>
<P>The Fir&s;t on April 23d, in the SCOTS PRESBYTERIAN CHURCH, BY THE REV. DR. LIVINGSTON.</P>
<P>The Second on April 24th, in the NORTH DUTCH CHURCH, BY THE REV. DR. M'KNIGHT; TO WHICH IS ADDED, A CHARGE given to the FIRST MISSIONARY, BY THE REV. DR. RODGERS; TOGETHER WITH THE INSTRUCTIONS TO MISSIONARIES, AND THE REPORT OF THE DIRECTORS.</P>
