<P>THAT the thanks of the SOCIETY be given to the Rev. Dr. LIVINGSTON and Dr. M'KNIGHT, for the Sermons delivered by them re&s;pectively on the evenings of the 23d and 24th in&s;t. agreeably to appointment; and that they be reque&s;ted to furni&s;h copies of the &s;ame for publication.</P>
